---
config:
  theme: white
  themeVariables:
    background: '#ffffff'
    primaryColor: '#ffffff'
    primaryTextColor: '#000000'
    lineColor: '#000000'
    secondaryColor: '#ffffff'
    tertiaryColor: '#ffffff'
    actorBorder: '#000000'
    actorTextColor: '#000000'
  look: classic
  mirrorActors: true
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor App as Application (Startup)
    participant DCM as DatabaseManager
    participant DB@{ "type": "database" } as Database

    App->>DCM: get_instance()
    activate DCM
    DCM->>DCM: shared instance exists?
    Note right of DCM: No instance found.
    DCM->>DCM: run creation procedure
    activate DCM
    DCM->>DCM: read connection configuration
    DCM->>DB: establish connection pool
    activate DB
    DB-->>DCM: connection pool ready
    deactivate DB
    DCM->>DCM: configure session factory
    DCM->>DCM: store object in shared variable
    deactivate DCM
    DCM-->>App: return instance (new DatabaseConnectionManager)
    deactivate DCM
    Note right of App: Singleton created and cached. Engine and session factory are ready.